{"tid":1381914,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到有人話班𡃁仔冇錢食飯，我有個提議⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-07-29T10:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:30:49.000Z","uid":43959,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e3208f1356232ea512f776b081c2f265f278f096","tid":1381914,"uid":43959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"我認為可以有心支援嘅餐廳/士多可以貼張貼紙喺門口，表示有需要嘅行動者可以免費食飯。<br />\n<br />\n為保安全，大家講個信字，唔使表明自己身份，只需向店鋪講「我要食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」即可<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似買待用飯劵俾班長者咁，買十張飯劵、鋪頭出面就寫有十張，大家見字即可入去開餐，有錢嘅就得閒去呢啲餐廳俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家知道有餐廳肯加入做義士食堂就留低個名整張List<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個方法未必好安全，歡迎大家補充指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3c9a73941c954f9a39b45b77bc980ca5bf26c1","tid":1381914,"uid":198245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"64dda8d891ae4cd2d03a8006b7369a65f9a8a1ad","tid":1381914,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NX7EMKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNX7EMKA.jpg&h=990f4b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEiXypB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEiXypB.jpg&h=020f3ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ans9pwg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAns9pwg.png&h=b8d6d814&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b365970d06285f3b75839b8d0ae55f10a26f9d5","tid":1381914,"uid":128298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2